f=Brand Studio/tempo/operational/agent/tempo-config.md · p=Machine-readable configuration for tempo. · h2:Config Template=`# --- Per brand --- \· brands: \· - brand_id: <FILL_IN> \· audio_active: <FILL_IN>          # yes/no — no = tempo is a documented no-op for this brand \· sonic_guide_path: <FILL_IN>      # the approved guide (from the template); required if active` · in=`audio_active: no` skills no-op explicitly; structure stays uniform. Active without guide/registry build/acquisition loops run before any content ships audio. · f=Unfilled config degrades loudly, never silently.